  <summary date="2017-01-24T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Better Agriculture Resources Now Act or the BARN Act

This bill revises the H-2A nonimmigrant agricultural worker visa program, including with respect to: (1) agricultural labor and services, (2) application requirements, (3) wages, (4) period of authorized nonimmigrant status, (5) housing, (6) legal assistance, and (7) violations.</summary>
